detail: Introducing R1 HD, the newest member of the BLU smartphone family. The new R1 HD promises performance, power, and style.

Introducing Scinex SW20 highest quality Smartwatch. Now you can easily make and answer phone calls whenever you like even when your phone isn't nearby. You can read and reply to SMS messages (on Android Only), receive notifications like WhatsApp and Emails, and stream your favorite music straight from your smartphone device. Taking photos and videos are easy, and with a 16GB memory capacity, you will have plenty of space for them all.

This case is a 3-piece case that delivers protection in style. The soft inner TPU layer protects the phone from scratches that would otherwise occur from contactof the sliding PC panels. These hard polycarbonate panels slide seamlessly across the TPU layer, locking with each other for a secure fit that’s thin.ATTENTION! Both pieces are held firmly together only when the phone is inside the case.
